</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_119_r2l18"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>H<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>vıcʒtu<ex>m</ex></expan> als vns eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> vor vnd yecʒ <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von yoſep </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r2l19">pücʒels des Juden <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der bey vns wonhaft <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ıſt etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r2l20">wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> yoſep auf eẅr <expan>vord<ex>er</ex></expan> brief </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r2l21">müntlıch <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> / So tun wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . daʒ wır <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r2l23">yoſep Juden . von <expan>merklıch<ex>er</ex></expan> klag 
<add><ab facs="#facs_119_r2l22">vnd ſachen </ab></add> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe für vns <expan>v̈b<ex>er</ex></expan> Jn kam dar </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r2l27">Jnn er ſıch 
<add><ab facs="#facs_119_line_1577029097608_1203">bey vns </ab></add> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>handelt</expan> vnd wol gröſſer ſtraff verſchuldt hett . gepüſſet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r2l28"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>Dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſtraffe ʒuhalten . er iren Jüdıſchen eyde geſworn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r2l29">vnd <expan>Jnſtrume<ex>n</ex>t</expan> v̈ber ſıch <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat / Ob keinrley bett für Jn beſchehe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_119_r2l30">daʒ Jn das daran niht <expan>fürtrage<ex>n</ex></expan> ſol . Aber <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒulıeb </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_120" id="59r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r1l1">ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır ſeinem weıb ſeinen kınden vnd <expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒweyen <expan>brüd<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Davıd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r1l2">vnd <expan>ſelıgma<ex>n</ex></expan> den Juden geleyt bey vns <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſand Jacobs tag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r1l3"><expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıchen</expan> . Doch alſo Ob dıe ʒeıt ıcht darein fıel . daʒ es vns niht fük = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r1l4">lıch würde / Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır Jn acht tag beuor ʒu wıſſen tun . Denn wo vvır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_line_1577029138847_1245"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Joh<ex>ann</ex>ıs</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_r1l7"><expan>Porta<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Latina<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
